<%= provide(:title, "Contract")%>
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "contracts.css" %> 
<br/>
<h1> CONTRACT</h1>
<p3> <u><%= @contract.service_buyer.name%></u>, known as "First Party," agrees to enter into this contract with <u><%= @contract.service_provider.name %></u> , known as "Second Party" on {date}.
This agreement is based on the following terms: <br/><br/>
1. <%= @contract.bid.offer %><br/><br/>
2. Price:  <%= @contract.amount %><br/><br/>
3. Service Level Provided: <%= @contract.service_level %><br/><br/>
Furthermore, the First Party agrees:{other items applicable to the First Party} and the Second Party agrees:{other items applicable to the Second Party} .
Invalidity or unenforceability of one or more provisions of this agreement shall not affect any other provision of this agreement.
This agreement is subject to the laws and regulations of the state of Aalto University. <br/><br/><br/>
Signed: <br/>
<br/>
<u><%= @contract.service_buyer.name %></u>
<span style="padding-left:505px"> <em><u> <p4><%= @contract.service_buyer.name%> </p4></u></em></span> <br/>
{First Party Name}
<span style="padding-left:495px">{First Party Signature}<br/></span>
<br/>
<br/>
<u><%= @contract.service_provider.name %></u>
<span style="padding-left:485px"> <em><u> <p4><%= @contract.service_provider.name %></p4> </u></em></span> <br/>
{Second Party Name}
<span style="padding-left:470px">{Second Party Signature}</span>
<% unless @contract.under_negotiation || current_user.isTeacher? %>
<div id="negotiation_form">
<div class="row">
  <div class="span6 offset3">
  <%= form_for(@contract) do |f| %>
      <%= render 'shared/error_messages', :object => f.object %>
      
      <%= f.label :new_amount, "New Price" %>
      <%= f.text_field :new_amount %>

     <%= f.label :new_service_level, "New Service Level" %>
      <%= f.text_field :new_service_level %>

      <%= f.submit "Send re-negotiation request", class: "btn btn-large btn-primary" %>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
 </div>
</div>
</div>

<% if !current_user.isTeacher? %> 
<button class ="btn btn-primary" id="negotiation_button">Re-negotiate contract </button>
<%end%>

<% if @contract.under_negotiation && !current_user.isTeacher? && current_user.company == @contract.negotiation_receiver %>
<p> <%= @contract.negotiation_sender.name %> wishes to re-negotiate the contract with following changes: </p>
<ul>
  <li> New Price: <%= @contract.new_amount %> </li>
  <li> New Service Level: <%= @contract.new_service_level %> </li>
</ul>
<div class="left_button">
 <%= form_tag contract_decision_path do %>
     <%= hidden_field_tag("decision", "ACC") %>
      <%= submit_tag "Accept", class: "btn btn-success" %>
 <% end %>
</div>

<div class="right_button">
    <%=  form_tag contract_decision_path do  %>
     <%= hidden_field_tag("decision", "REJ") %>
      <%= submit_tag "Decline", class: "btn btn-danger" %>
    <% end %>
</div>
<% end %>

